content: अनुत्तर {%<ab>a.</ab>%} [नास्ति उत्तरो यस्मात्] {@--1@} Principal, chief. {@--2@} Best, excellent; अनुत्तराणि विलसितानि <ls>Dk. 162</ls> unsurpassed. {@--3@} [नास्ति उत्तरं यस्य] Without a reply, silent, unable to answer; भवत्यवज्ञा च भवत्यनुत्तरात् <ls>Naiṣadha.</ls> {@--4@} Fixed, firm (न उत्तरति चलति). {@--5@} Low, inferior, base, mean. {@--6@} Southern. --रं [न. त.] No reply, a reply which, being evasive, is considered to be no reply. --राः (<ab>pl.</ab>) A class of gods among Jainas (°उपपातिक). --रा The south.
